•handful of ice
•1/2 frozen banana🍌
•1 cup frozen berries (i love blueberry🫐)
•1 scoop protein powder
•1 scoop collagen peptides
•1 tbsp ground flax seeds
•1 tbsp chia seeds
•1 tbsp MCT oil
•big a$$ spoonfuls of peanut or almond butter🥜🍯
•handful of spinach🥝 
•water or nut milk for desired thickness

LITTLE BITES MUFFIN WEEK IS HERE! #rachLlittlebitesweek to be exact👌🏻day one we are kicking it off with the classic mini blueberry muffins. i used to have these in my lunch box as a kid and would beg my mom for more (blueberries.. you know that meant they’re healthier😂)
